OL,7,FThe families of children who were
OL,8,Fdrugged and sexually abused by 'vile'
OL,9,Fcamp leader Jon Ruben say they feel
OL,10,Fbetrayed and that he has 'ruined their
OL,11,Flives'.
OL,13,FRuben pleaded guilty to sexual assault
OL,14,Fof a child under 13, assault of a
OL,15,Fchild under 13 by penetration, eight
OL,16,Fcounts of child cruelty, three counts
OL,17,Fof making indecent images of children
OL,18,Fand four drugs charges.
OL,20,FHe has been jailed for 23 years and
OL,21,Ften months.
