OL,3,CFamilies of children abused by
OL,4,C'creature' Jon Ruben say lives have
OL,5,Cbeen ruined
OL,7,FIt happened at Stathern Lodge near
OL,8,FMelton. The 76-year-old played a game
OL,9,Fwhere he'd go into the boys rooms and
OL,10,Fencourage them to eat the sweets as
OL,11,Fquickly as possible.
OL,13,FRuben had been running the holiday
OL,14,Fcamp for 27 years. He was a volunteer
OL,15,Fat St Peter's Church in Ruddington and
OL,16,Fin local schools.
OL,18,FThe court heard Ruben also drugged his
OL,19,Fwife so she would sleep heavily and
OL,20,Fdid not wake up during his offending
OL,21,Fagainst the boys.
