OL,14,FLeicester Crown Court: "As one mother
OL,15,Fhas accurately said, there's only one
OL,16,Fperson to blame for this, and that is
OL,17,FJon Ruben. That is the reality."
OL,19,FRuben's barrister Thomas Schofield KC
OL,20,Fsaid the defendant had described
